2026-05-04T00:09:49.4630586Z             "body": "## Summary\nThis PR makes two improvements to the web application: disabling automatic translation of the UI across all HTML pages, and fixing a bug in DKIM selector initialization logic.\n\n## Key Changes\n- Added `translate=\"no\"` attribute to the `<html>` tag in all four HTML pages (index.html, config.html, login.html, tokens.html) to prevent browser translation services from translating the application UI\n- Fixed DKIM selectors initialization in index.html to check for non-empty array before populating the input field, preventing unnecessary processing of empty arrays\n\n## Implementation Details\nThe DKIM selectors fix adds a length check (`o.dkimSelectors.length > 0`) to the existing `Array.isArray()` validation. This ensures that the custom DKIM selectors input field and the `dkimUserCustomized` flag are only set when there are actual selectors to process, improving the robustness of the configuration loading logic.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01HQsfAXid9F8X7vcjWgbkK1",
